-----------
| Files |
________________________________________________________________________________________________________

img/			| contains site images
js/ 			| contains site javascript
	Lightbox.js		| Lightbox class - adds "toggleable" layers to the page
	main.js			| mootools domready event code
	mootools-*core.js 	| latest mootools core 
	mootools-*more.js	| latest mootools more
php/ 		| contains site php code other than index.php
	includes.php		| class includes and session initialization
	login.php			| simple php login script using the User and Database classes
	signup.php		| simple php signup script using the User and Database classes
phpClasses/ 	| contains php classes
	Database			| DatabaseConnection class
	Filters			| User input filtering class
	User				| Class for user management (add, authenticate, update or remove)
SQL/ 		| for reference: any SQL statements needed for site database
style/ 		| CSS style file(s)
index.php		| main site
README		| this file
